Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(566,454)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天肉饼翻得可优秀了  铲铲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice flipping today, Spatty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你烤得真棒  架架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great grill work, Grilly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少了你我肯定做不到  火火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we couldn't have done it without you, Flamey
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.75,0:01:13.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:13.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gallopin' garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.10,0:01:24.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没见过蟹堡王到处都是脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,covered in this much filth
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然你说下水道居民来开大会能咋样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you expect from a Sewer Dwellers' convention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016,168)}下水道居民  本地{\fnArial}396{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}号
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲餐桌礼仪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,table manners?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.98,0:01:30.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:30.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也待得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've had enough
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以不用回下水道去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go back to the sewer
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但就是不准待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you can't stay here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.03,0:01:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're closed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走之前  把蟹堡王打扫干净
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, make sure this place is spotless before you leave
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.45,0:01:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ay-yi-yi
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下得通宵打扫了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to take me all night
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上开始扫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd better get started
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望能有个朋友帮忙清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:09.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a friend to help me clean this place up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好强的东风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Strong wind coming in from the east
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌  更确切地说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More specifically, I'd wager
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吹的是东北风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're coming in from the northeast
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在说话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did, Gov'ner
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拖拖  刚刚的着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moppy, that landing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从各方面来说都切实可行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was perfectly practical in every way
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是清道夫萨米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I'm Sammy Suckerfish
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也正是快乐清洁工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the jolly janitor I am, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,风中传来的消息说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the word on the wind is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你需要找帮手打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you need a little cleaning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, do I
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  拖拖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Moppy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.62,0:03:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  快看看那片可爱又可恨的脏污
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blimey, will you take a gander
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at all that lovely ruddy filth?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要先清理哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should we clean first?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.62,0:03:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我向来都会先清理餐厅的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I always like to start with the eyes of the eatery
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:17.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that meaning the windows
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些东西可以收起来了  老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can put those away, me old mucker
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那样还怎么擦窗户呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how are we going to wash the windows?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell ya
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有的清洁工清洁只会用板刷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are janitors who only clean with brushes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有的用抹布或扫把
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Others use a rag or cloth or broom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是归根结底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But when all is said and done
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发现用舌头最好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I find it best to use me tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.49,0:03:43.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,失陪一下  让我舔舔这房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:43.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So excuse me while I lick this room
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也试试舔舔看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now give your tongue a go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yuck
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,萨米  嘴里味道太难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sammy, that tastes horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about now?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在嘴里感觉不出味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can't taste anything
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鼻子没味  嘴里也会没味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you can't smell it, you can't taste it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to singing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污快快舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up lickety-split
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污统统舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up, every bit
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舔干净窗户  舔干净门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the windows, lick all the doors
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舔完天花板  又舔地板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick up the ceiling, lick up the floors
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舔干净脏污  就这么定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up, that's the plan
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污吐进垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spit out the dirt into the can
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里的脏污舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up in the place
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脸上的脏污舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up off your face
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我抹布再也无用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never use a cloth or rag again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舌头刷刷拖拖都特干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tongue can now out-clean or brush or mop
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他海绵宝宝  我萨米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's SpongeBob and I'm Sammy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不用皮革清理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We refuse to use a shammy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.56,0:04:59.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要一直舔个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:59.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're licking it up and we will never stop
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.16,0:05:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yum
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.58,0:05:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹小气  章鱼哥好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Krabs is cheap, Squidward smells"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥味道好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward smells great
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是要怎么清掉这堆涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how do we get this graffiti off?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有些污渍十分顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some stains are so tough
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.97,0:05:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得用一点点神奇皂粉对付
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they need a little-a bit-a magic soap
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,涂鸦变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,graffiti, boo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们要清死我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're gonna clean us to death--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是用我们自个的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with our own tongues
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没必要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,涂鸦变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:27.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Graffiti boo
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都清干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We cleaned everything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里肯定还有地方得清理  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's still more cleaning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,around here to do, love
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闻出脏污吧  乖拖拖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sniff out the dirt, Moppy old girl
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小眼睛看到了这间肮脏房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I spy with my little eye this filthy room
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板不准外人进他办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs doesn't like anybody in his office
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的蟹老板肯定不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your Mr. Krabs wouldn't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们帮他整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if we tidied up a bit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,墙上都是杂物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These walls are chock-full of clutter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是萨米  那都是蟹老板的私有财产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Sammy, that's Mr. Krabs's private property
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,萨米  那样会有大麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sammy, we're gonna get in big trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别清保险柜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the safe
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.88,0:07:30.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:30.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别清秘密配方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not the secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Secret formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1280,388)}秘密配方
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清道夫萨米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sammy Suckerfish
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上把秘密配方吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you spit out that secret formula this instant
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.61,0:07:51.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都说过了  我一清理就停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:51.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't stop cleaning
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,萨米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sammy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举起手来  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hands up, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经包围你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you surrounded--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,萨米  住嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sammy, stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫过他住嘴了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told him to stop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站一边去  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step aside, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know what's going on here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evening, Gov'ner
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你的英国佬假脑袋摘下来  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take off that phony British head, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你谁都骗不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not fooling anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定就在里面  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上给我滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, get out of there already
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,596)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep it down
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.29,0:08:42.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱这边一大早还得偷秘密配方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some people have to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,steal the secret formula in the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果他不是痞老板  那他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If he's not Plankton, then who is he?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是个神奇清洁工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's a magical janitor
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还刚舔走了你保险柜门和里面的秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that licked off your safe door
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the secret formula with it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(526,484)}秘密配方
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give that back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No worries, gents
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个保险柜可干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That safe is as clean as a whistle
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  拖拖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Moppy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隆重介绍小拖拖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Introducing the Moppettes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污快快舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up lickety-split
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污统统舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up, every bit
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舔干净窗户  舔干净门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the windows, lick all all the doors
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方还是印在他舌头上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's still got the secret formula stuck to his tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要把秘方抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get the formula back
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想得美  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you don't, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方抢不回来  我也会完蛋的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a stake in this, too, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暂时休战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Temporary truce
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拦住那根舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop that tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.27,0:09:45.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:45.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.56,0:09:45.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:45.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Double time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污快快舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up lickety-split
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污统统舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up, every bit
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舔干净窗户  舔干净门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the windows, lick all the doors
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舔完天花板  又舔地板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:58.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick up the ceiling, lick up the floors
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舔干净脏污  就这么定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up, that's the plan
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污吐进垃圾桶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spit out the dirt into the can
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里的脏污舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up in the place
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脸上的脏污舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up off your face
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别那么用力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so hard
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.04,0:10:12.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脏污快快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:12.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lick all the dirt up--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  萨米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sammy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们需要你的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we need your tongue
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.88,0:10:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早说过了  我一清理就停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't stop cleaning
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,萨米  你身上有污渍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sammy, you have smudges all over you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,污渍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A smudge?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.15,0:10:30.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:30.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On me?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.31,0:10:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就要来洗澡了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then, I suppose it's bath time, innit?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好玩吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was fun, eh, Spongey?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  可别说我什么都没给过你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, and don't say I never give you nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(568,560)}秘密配方
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The formula
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:00.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Gov'ner
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑一个  秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say cheese, secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清理掉那个肮脏小坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean that dirty little scoundrel
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope it's clear
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么关门后不让陌生人进来  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why we don't let strangers in after closing time, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清楚明白  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干净又明了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crystal clear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.22,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFA3&}神厨大联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,372)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:50.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(632,450)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,648)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.69,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.81,0:11:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发现咱特别需要找个新大厨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware that we need a new super chef
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(612,374)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我们新开的体育场大餐厅下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the big, new stadium restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.28,0:12:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这边已经发现了三个潜在的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found three potential candidates
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要再找一个就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I just need one more
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那人必须活力四射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,someone with pizzazz
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别活力了  好好做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you cut the pizzazz and finish the order?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  我先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, I gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚的厨艺太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's some mighty fancy cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that my order?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有什么瑕疵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong with it?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竟然会问里面有没有瑕疵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong, he says
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就是完美无瑕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only everything right with it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与其在这家小破店上班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here in this greasy dump
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.66,0:12:58.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不如来大联盟当神厨明星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you could be a culinary superstar
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the big leagues?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.13,0:12:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是你老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's your manager?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板是我老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is my manager
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吵什么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's all that rumpus in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这小丑鱼是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is this clownfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.34,0:13:10.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这小丑鱼要让你发大财
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:10.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This clownfish is gonna make you a very wealthy crab
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.64,0:13:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神厨体育场大餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Culinary Stadium Restaurant?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.02,0:13:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个全新又大胆的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a bold new concept
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:20.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,194)}神厨体育场
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把棒球场改造成了餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've converted a baseball stadium into a restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以同时为上千名食客服务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,serving thousands of food fans at the same time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以要付你多少钱才能把这位新手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So how much to take this greenhorn
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这只菜鸟  这艘身上全是洞的小船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this rookie, this dinghy full of holes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.83,0:13:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从你蟹爪中带走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,off of your claws?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,领带都被食物弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food stains on his tie
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deplorable
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not deplorable--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会跟我员工分开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could never part ways with me--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉刚刚胡言乱语了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon my vapors
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.39,0:13:55.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板  我不想离开蟹堡王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:55.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs, I don't want to leave the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不是我想不让你留下  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, far be it from me to hold you back, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过看在这么多钱的情况嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the looks of this legal tender
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很明显你命中注定要追求远大前程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's obvious you're destined
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for bigger and better things
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油吧  大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get 'em, hotshot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊艳大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock 'em dead
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊艳大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock 'em dead
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:26.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070,526)}选拔厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  你们这群小厨子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, you lowly hash slingers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是选拔厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the tryout kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.63,0:14:32.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们四个要互相竞争厨艺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The four of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will compete cooking against each other
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,期间会一个接一个地淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be eliminated one by one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后只会有一位厨子能留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until there's only one of you left standing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有且只有那个厨子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That person and only that person
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以为全场下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will cook for the whole stadium
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且荣获神厨头衔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and receive the title of super chef
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,淘汰会有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happens when you're eliminated?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.78,0:14:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要上高速公路卖脏水热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be selling dirty water hot dogs on the freeway
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:59.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,414)}高速入口
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like fun
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握个手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put her there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卷卷手指薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curly finger fries
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点开始了  你们这群菜鸟厨子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, go, go, you goofy gourmets
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉汤和食材都提供给大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got your broth, and you got your ingredients
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要品尝到独一无二的汤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to taste a soup that's unique
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还要有非凡的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a flavor that's singular
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哎哟喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw, gee
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.95,0:15:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你调料都没固定好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you ain't got no fixings for mix-ins
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.66,0:15:40.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样很过分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:40.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not fair
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要听浪漫晚宴音乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some romantic dinner music?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道你汤里缺什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what your soup needs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要加点粗纤维
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little roughage
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来帮你搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me "nail" it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1124,920)}钉
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩十秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten seconds left
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:57.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,领带都被食物弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food stains on his tie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的领带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My tie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡一泡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dunk, dunk
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.78,0:16:12.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:12.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可以有钉子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nails are unacceptable
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not good, but not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.31,0:16:48.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清淡提神  里面还混有人造纤维
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:48.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Light, refreshing with just a hint of rayon
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本轮海绵获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This round goes to the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  你们这群菜鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up, you gruff guppies
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一关是披萨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next challenge is pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.91,0:17:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要的披萨必须无与伦比  意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a pizza that's extraordinary, unanticipated
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出人意料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from left field--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许有钉子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and no nails
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  之前的事真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, buddy, I'm sorry about before
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来补偿一下你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me make it up to you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.93,0:17:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用我妈的秘方特制了这份披萨面团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've made this special pizza dough
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from me old mother's recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to have it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Much obliged
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有薄荷味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Minty
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就这么喜欢钉子是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you like nails, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竟敢偷我奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stealing my cheese, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对付你这种小虾米  我自有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know just what to do with shrimps like you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只虾怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to the shrimp?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是抗压能力太弱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess some folks can't handle the pressure
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老龟  到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turtle, you're up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没钉子的事我怎么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I say about no nails?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你杠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It had to be you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.81,0:18:14.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死都要找你报仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:14.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get back at you if it's the last thing I do
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,形状独特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unusual shape
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有薄荷  热带浆果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hints of mint, tropical berry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉桂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cinnamon
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这又是什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what's this flavor?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shrimp
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱往披萨加虾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love shrimp on pizza
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选拔赛结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The competition is over
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你打出全垒打了  海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you hit a home run, sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入大联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the big leagues
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连从未有过的梦想居然都能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even the dreams that you've never had can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:04.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(952,418)}神厨体育场
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临神厨体育场  食客们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Culinary Stadium, food fans
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就要开始下厨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The cooking is about to begin
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.70,0:19:08.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位食客  请大家热烈欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:08.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Food fans, will you please give a warm welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.37,0:19:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新任神厨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to our new super chef, SpongeBob SquarePants?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1014,278)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.59,0:19:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你了  冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's you, champ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一鸣惊人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock it out of the park
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一鸣惊人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock it out of the park
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's cook
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先要做的是  焦糖海草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First up, caramelized kelp
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,青酱珊瑚  以及巧克力烤藻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pesto coral, and grilled chocolate algae
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菜鸟迎来了个开门红
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The rookie is off to a great start
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他表现十分出彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's showing excellent form
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看那小子的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at the arm on that kid
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油炸海香蕉  金箔面包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fried sea bananas, the gold flake breadsticks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,培根卷豆角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,twigs in a blanket
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.09,0:20:06.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝下厨绝对一流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is handling all the orders
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like a true champion
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就说我会找他报仇的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told him I'd get him back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方怎么没桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are there no tables up here?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.74,0:20:26.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐桌只给下面高级区的阔佬用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The tables with food are for the wealthy moneybags
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:26.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down below in the premium section
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只能眼睁睁看别人吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We only get to watch 'em eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,技巧如此之高超灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such skill, such agility
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但他能否跟上速度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But can he keep up the pace?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菜鸟的点餐单越积越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The orders are piling up for our rookie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我们的小子有麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like our boy is in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厨房已经满负荷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All food bases are loaded
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给海绵宝宝送点餐单
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm giving SpongeBob an order
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他有它稳赢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know he can win with
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.24,0:21:05.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来神厨接到了一项特别订单
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:05.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like our chef has a special order, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这美食好像有些俗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That doesn't look like gourmet food
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time-out
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该做的是高级菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be cooking high-class cuisine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是快餐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not fast food
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  谢谢你给我机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, thanks for the opportunity
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我还是宁愿留在蟹堡联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I like it better in the Krusty leagues
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我弃赛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forfeit
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这年头的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These kids today
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还消极比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No respect for the game
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定会爆红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're blowing up big-time
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you hear 'em?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.75,0:21:57.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:57.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go out there
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鞠出最后一躬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take your final bow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鞠出最后一躬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take your final bow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他到底哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where the heck does he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.81,0:22:15.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:15.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.65,0:22:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.03,0:22:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的小子回归了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our boy's come back to us
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.53,0:22:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是早说你会爆红的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you you were blowing up?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.20,0:22:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure did, kid
